---
title: Pork with Peach Thyme Pan Sauce with Zesty Zucchini & Almond Garlic Couscous
description: We’re big fans of pan sauces because they’re an easy way to make a great dish completely irresistible. Here, peach jam, rich chicken stock, tangy Dijon, and fresh thyme mingle to create a condiment that you’ll want to drizzle over everything. Speaking of, along with the juicy pork cutlets, we’re serving up sides of garlicky, almond-flecked couscous and simply roasted zucchini for maximum dinnertime deliciousness.
